val cloud_elems = sc.textFile("hdfs://scispark1.jpl.nasa.gov:8090/data/notebook_data/cloudElementsTab.txt")
val cloud_elems_nospace = cloud_elems.filter(line => !line.isEmpty)
case class CloudElement(lat: Float, lon: Float, time: String, area: Float, uid: Int)
val cloud_elements = cloud_elems_nospace.map(line => line.split(",")).map(line => CloudElement(line(0).toFloat,line(1).toFloat,line(2),line(3).toFloat,line(4).toInt))
val data_frame = cloud_elements.toDF()
data_frame.registerTempTable("cloud_elems_table")

val slices = 1000
val n= math.min(100000L * slices, Int.MaxValue).toInt //avoid overflow
val count = sc.parallelize(1 until n, slices).map { i =>
    val x = Math.random() * 2 -1
    val y = Math.random() * 2 -1
    if (x*x + y*y < 1) 1 else 0
}.reduce(_ + _)
println("\nPi is roughly " + 4.0 * count / n)
